                        </div>
                        <h3>Voice Channels</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="rule-list-modern">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> No mic spamming or playing music without permission</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Use push-to-talk if you have background noise</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Respect others in voice chat</li>
                    </ul>
